<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>

    <meta charset="UTF-8">

    <meta name="viewport"
          content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>NetFix AI</title>

    <style>

        *{
            margin:0;
            padding:0;
            box-sizing:border-box;
        }

        body{
            background:#0f172a;
            color:white;
            font-family:Arial, sans-serif;
            overflow-x:hidden;
        }

        .hero{

            height:100vh;

            display:flex;
            flex-direction:column;

            justify-content:center;
            align-items:center;

            text-align:center;

            padding:20px;
        }

        h1{

            font-size:65px;

            color:#38bdf8;

            margin-bottom:20px;

            text-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(56,189,248,0.4);
        }

        .subtitle{

            font-size:22px;

            color:#cbd5e1;

            max-width:850px;

            line-height:1.7;
        }

        .highlight{
            color:#38bdf8;
            font-weight:bold;
        }

        .features{

            margin-top:50px;

            display:flex;

            gap:25px;

            flex-wrap:wrap;

            justify-content:center;
        }

        .card{

            background:#1e293b;

            border:1px solid #334155;

            width:280px;

            padding:25px;

            border-radius:16px;

            transition:0.3s;
        }

        .card:hover{

            transform:translateY(-5px);

            border-color:#38bdf8;

            box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(56,189,248,0.2);
        }

        .card h3{

            color:#38bdf8;

            margin-bottom:15px;

            font-size:22px;
        }

        .card p{

            color:#cbd5e1;

            line-height:1.6;
        }

        .status{

            margin-top:35px;

            color:#22c55e;

            font-size:18px;
        }

        .footer{

            position:absolute;

            bottom:20px;

            width:100%;

            text-align:center;

            color:#64748b;

            font-size:14px;
        }

        .glow{

            position:absolute;

            width:500px;
            height:500px;

            background:#0ea5e9;

            opacity:0.08;

            border-radius:50%;

            filter:blur(100px);

            z-index:-1;
        }

        .glow1{
            top:-150px;
            left:-150px;
        }

        .glow2{
            bottom:-150px;
            right:-150px;
        }

    </style>

</head>

<body>

    <div class="glow glow1"></div>
    <div class="glow glow2"></div>

    <section class="hero">

        <h1>🌐 NetFix AI</h1>

        <p class="subtitle">

            Intelligent <span class="highlight">AI-powered network troubleshooting assistant</span>
            built for diagnosing internet connectivity issues,
            Wi-Fi failures, DNS problems, VPN errors,
            routing issues, and network command diagnostics.

        </p>

        <div class="features">

            <div class="card">

                <h3>🌍 Internet Diagnostics</h3>

                <p>
                    Detect connectivity failures,
                    packet loss,
                    ISP issues,
                    and high latency problems instantly.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="card">

                <h3>📶 Wi-Fi & Router Support</h3>

                <p>
                    Troubleshoot wireless connectivity,
                    DNS failures,
                    gateway problems,
                    and router misconfigurations.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="card">

                <h3>🛠 Command Analysis</h3>

                <p>
                    Analyze outputs from
                    ping,
                    tracert,
                    ipconfig,
                    nslookup,
                    netstat,
                    and more.
                </p>

            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="status">
            ● NetFix AI is online and ready to troubleshoot
        </div>

    </section>

    <div class="footer">
        NetFix AI • AI-Powered Network Troubleshooting Platform
    </div>



